column2:
Percipio users: If you are a Percipio user looking for the Bootcamp class slides and the attendance tracker, please use following these steps. 

1. Open a new tab or browser window and log into Percipio
2. Select Library > Showcase > Skillsoft Bootcamps
3. Choose Project Management Bootcamps
4. Select Project Management Professional (PMP) ATP Bootcamp: 8 Day UK Cohort
5. The Resources tab includes the Bootcamp class slides, attendance tracker, and so on

Non-Percipio and Percipio Users: You can access documents including the session slides and attendance tracker from GitHub.

https://github.com/Skillsoft-Content/PMP8Day

Note: Click Code and then Download Zip to get all resources from GitHub. Tracker document is called: PMP Bootcamp 5-Day and 8-Day Attendance Tracker and Certificate Request Process

column2: how is possible to download the slides?
column5:
The course files have been uploaded to the Bootcamp Channel in Percipio. Please visit the Bootcamp Channel in Percipio and select the Resources drop-down to locate the course files. 
 
To locate the Bootcamp Channel in Percipio, please follow these steps:
1. Log into Percipio
2. Select Library > Showcase > Skillsoft Bootcamps > Project Management Bootcamps
3. Select the 'Project Management Professional (PMP) ATP Bootcamp: 8 Day UK Cohort' channel
4. On the Channel page, select 'Resources'
 
You may also download the course files online at GitHub using the below URL. Once on the GitHub page, download the course files by selecting the ‘Code’ button and then ‘Download ZIP’. 
https://github.com/Skillsoft-Content/PMP8Day

4. On the Channel page, select 'Resources'
 
You may also download the course files online at GitHub using the below URL. Once on the GitHub page, download the course files by selecting the ‘Code’ button and then ‘Download ZIP’. 
https://github.com/Skillsoft-Content/PMP8Day

column2: Please help with details on the Learner Kit as well
column5: Please help with details on the Learner Kit as well

column2: Please help with details on the Learner Kit as well
column5:
Taking the Bootcamp is free but all participants in Skillsoft’s ATP-authorized PMP Bootcamps who intend to sit for the PMP certification exam are required to purchase a PMP Learner Kit. The Learner Kit can be purchased for $119 USD. Please note that the Learner Kit is not required for participants who are attending the Bootcamp for reasons other than taking the exam, such as expanding their project management knowledge, or earning continuing education credit.   

The Learner Kit comes with:
	• Student Manual
	• Project Manager Checklists
	• Student Resources
	• Post-Class Survey
	• Spotlight Videos
	• Self-Knowledge Check
	• And some other items
 
The following article has additional information on obtaining your learner kit.
https://community.skillsoft.com/kb/s/article/PMI-Certification-and-PDU-credits-Percipio 

You can purchase a learner kit from the following web page on the Skillsoft website:
https://www.skillsoft.com/pmp-voucher-offering

To locate the Bootcamp Channel in Percipio, please follow these steps:
1. Log into Percipio

3. Select the 'Project Management Professional (PMP) ATP Bootcamp: 8 Day UK Cohort' channel
4. On the Channel page, select 'Resources'

column2: Hi, is this Project Economy video available in the resources as well?
column5:
The short videos the instructor plays during the sessions are from the 2021 Update Courses. Percipio users can access the 2021 Update courses through their Bootcamp channel as follows.  
Step 1. Log into Percipio 
Step 2. Select Library > Showcase > Skillsoft Bootcamps 
Step 3. Choose Project Management Bootcamps 
Step 4. Select the Project Management Professional (PMP) ATP Bootcamp: UK and APAC Step 5. Where you see PMP ATP: PMP ATPv click the dropdown arrow "v" and select the Project Management Professional Certification (PMP) (2021 Update Aligned) option .
Step 6. The 2021 Update courses with the selected videos are on the Watch tab. Each slide indicates the selected course and the video from that course.  For all other users try searching your Learning Portal using the key words 2021 Update

column5:
It can take up to 14 business days to receive your certificate by email once you have submitted your request.

You may use the following site to calculate the business days between two dates:
https://www.timeanddate.com/date/workdays.html
 
If you haven't received your certificate by the end of the 14th business day, please do the following:
1. Check the Spam or Junk folder for the email address you used when filling out your profile for the certificate request to see if the email is in that folder.
2. If it's not in your Spam or Junk folder please email certificate.requests@skillsoft.com for a status update as they will have access to submitted requests to assist you further.

Percipio users: If you are a Percipio user looking for the Bootcamp class slides and the attendance tracker, please use following these steps.   1. Open a new tab or browser window and log into Percipio 2. Select Library > Showcase > Skillsoft Bootcamps 3. Choose Project Management Bootcamps 4. Select Project Management Professional (PMP) ATP Bootcamp: 8 Day UK Cohort 5. The Resources tab includes the Bootcamp class slides, attendance tracker, and so on  Non-Percipio and Percipio Users: You can access documents including the session slides and attendance tracker from GitHub.  https://github.com/Skillsoft-Content/PMP8Day  

For recording please contact Mentoring Team (mentoring@skillsoft.com)
